1 Day Ago Community leaders suggested that the disaster was due to the desecration of a sacred shrine by Fulani herders who had intruded into the shrine of the ancient deity. Despite the supernatural interpretation by the traditionalists, police said the thunderstorm that killed the cows was natural. It was gathered that the cows were struck dead at the rocky elevation said to be sacred to the community.